ARMS - ACADEMIC RECORD MANAGEMENT SYSTEM
      ARMS - Academic Record Management System was designed to facilitate the academic and administrative wings of University including 
  O/o Dean (CEG,ACT,MIT,SAP), Academic Courses, Departments, Placement (CUIC).
  It provides Time based locking facility and publication of results On-time.
  Quick dissemination of information regarding - status of each student to all stakeholders (based on role)









SEMS - STUDENT EXAMINATION MANAGEMENT SYSTEM

      Student Examination Management System (SEMS) is in-house software, where the faculty and students relevant data regarding enrolment, time table, course work, continuous assessment and end semester marks, grades,  etc. 
  are managed for all the programmes of the University.SEMS is maintained by the ACOE with technical team.













